      <title>消息人士称，苹果、Meta、谷歌将面临欧盟数字市场法案调查</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-meta-google-set-face-eu-digital-markets-act-probes-sources-say-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士表示，预计欧盟反垄断监管机构将利用《数字市场法》赋予的权力对苹果、Meta Platforms 和 Alphabet 旗下的谷歌进行调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-meta-google-set-face-eu-digital-markets-act-probes-sources-say-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 15:48:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛资产管理公司为新基金筹集逾7亿美元资金</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/goldman-sachs-asset-management-raises-over-700-mln-new-fund-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛资产管理公司周四表示，已为一只新基金筹集了超过 7 亿美元，该基金将与外部管理人合作，寻找公共和私人市场的投资机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/goldman-sachs-asset-management-raises-over-700-mln-new-fund-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 15:40:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>彭博社法律报道称，苹果和谷歌将根据新的欧盟数字法面临调查</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-google-set-face-probes-under-new-eu-digital-law-bloomberg-law-reports-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《彭博社法律》周四报道，苹果和 Alphabet 旗下的谷歌将因遵守针对大型科技公司的新法律而面临欧盟调查，这为可能面临巨额罚款铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-google-set-face-probes-under-new-eu-digital-law-bloomberg-law-reports-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 15:34:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
