      <title>随着降息迫在眉睫，加拿大银行存款争夺战愈演愈烈</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/battle-canadian-bank-deposits-seen-heating-up-rate-cuts-loom-2024-03-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师和高管表示，随着客户将高收益固定收益产品的资金转移到风险较高的投资以寻求更好的回报，加拿大银行之间对客户存款的竞争预计将加剧，利率可能会下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/battle-canadian-bank-deposits-seen-heating-up-rate-cuts-loom-2024-03-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 14:57:29 GMT</pubDate>
