      <title>高乐氏 (Clorox) 将出售部分拉丁美洲业务；收取 2.33 亿美元费用</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/clorox-sell-some-latin-american-operations-take-233-mln-charge-2024-03-21/</link>
